        "If {{ai|Defile|Karthus}} has been learned, it will remain toggled on for ''Death Defied's'' entire duration."
      ],
      "notes": "* Upon {{tip|Death}}, '''Karthus''' loses all {{tip|debuff|status effects}} (inherently including {{tip|crowd control}} effects) that do not inherently persist through death.\n** An example for a debuff that does persist through death is {{cai|Blaze|Brand}}.\n* ''Death Defied'' will always trigger after {{tip|resurrection}} effects.\n** ''Death Defied'' will still trigger if '''Karthus''' is killed by the {{tip|Nexus Obelisk}}.\n* At the start of ''Death Defied'', '''Karthus''' is set to {{sti|health|{{as|1 health}}}}.\n** '''Karthus''' can still regenerate his health over the duration, but he will always die at the end of it.\n* After ''Death Defied'' ends, the corpse of '''Karthus''' will retain [[unit collision]] despite being dead on the ground.\n* '''Karthus' ''' [[health bar|mana bar]] drains over the duration of ''Death Defied'' as an indicator of his time remaining in this state.",
